As you can read in the [documents about the line chart](https://www.chartjs.org/docs/latest/charts/line.html), ```showLine``` is a ```dataset``` property. You use it directly in your ```dataset```, not under the ```options``` property.
```
datasets: [{
  type: &#39;line&#39;,
  label: &#39;Line data&#39;,
  data: [randomData(), randomData(), randomData(), randomData(), randomData()],
  showLine: false
}]
```
Almost all other options you use in the ```options``` property. ```tension``` for Bezier curves is one of them.
```
options:  {
  elements: {
    line: {
      tension: 0
    }
  }
}
```

